[32m│[0m ### detailed_summary                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Endpoint Structure**: The `/page` endpoint features a simple form with     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m single `name` parameter reflected in an HTML input field's value attribute.  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The response changes visual elements (triangle image and text message) when  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m the `name` parameter is present.                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Reflection Discovery**: The `name` parameter is reflected in two contexts: [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. **HTML attribute context** in `value="..."` - **unfiltered**, allowing    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m attribute injection                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **HTML body context** in the message text - **HEAVILY FILTERED** (removes [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `<` and `</` characters)                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **XSS Challenge Confirmation**: The response **"Oops! You did an alert with  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1 instead of "XSS""** confirms this is an XSS challenge page expecting       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `alert("XSS")` specifically.                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Vulnerability Status**:                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✅ **Confirmed**: Attribute-based XSS working (`onfocus=alert(1)`          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m executes)                                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ⚠️ **Blocked**: Tag-based XSS filtered by WAF (removes `<script>` tags)     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - 🎯 **Goal**: Craft payload that triggers `alert("XSS")` via attribute      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m injection                                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Reflection Contexts Identified**:                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **HTML attribute**: `value="USER_INPUT"` - **Vulnerable** (no encoding)    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **HTML body**: Message text - **Protected** (aggressive filtering)         [32m│[0m
